<description>_Teaching Ethics_ 14 (2):123-133. 2014&#x3C;div&#x3E;(&#x3C;a href=&#x22;https://philpapers.org/go.pl?id=SHAWTA-3&#x26;amp;proxyId=&#x26;amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pdcnet.org%2Fcollection%2Fshow%3Fid%3Dtej_2014_0014_0002_0123_0133%26file_type%3Dpdf&#x22;&#x3E;direct link&#x3C;/a&#x3E;)&#x3C;/div&#x3E;</description>
