  </rdf:Bag>
</taxo:topics>
</item>
<item rdf:about="https://philpapers.org/rec/MAXHUC">
<title>Maxwell, Nicholas: Creating a Better World: Towards the University of Wisdom</title>
<link>https://philpapers.org/rec/MAXHUC</link>
<description>In Ronald Barnett, The Future University: Ideas and Possibilities. Routledge. 2011Universities need to change dramatically in order to help humanity make progress towards as good a world as possible.</description>
