<item rdf:about="https://philpapers.org/rec/MAXAIT">
<title>Maxwell, Nicholas: An Idea to Save the World</title>
<link>https://philpapers.org/rec/MAXAIT</link>
<description>_Sublime_ (17):90-93. 2009Here is an idea that just might save the world. It is that science, properly understood, provides us with the methodological key to the salvation of humanity.</description>
